high_descs: Turn around and go towards the sink.
Pick the potato up from the sink.
Turn around and cross the room to face the fridge.
Put the potato in the fridge, shut the door and then open the door and pick the potato up and then shut the door.
Turn around and cross the room to face the trash can to the left of the counter.
Put the potato in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled potato in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around and walk across the kitchen to reach the sink.
Pick up the potato to the left of the sink.
Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Place the potato in the top section of the fridge, cool it, then take it out.
Turn around and walk to the trashcan to the left of the stove.
Place the potato in the trashcan.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooled potato in a trashcan.

high_descs: Turn to your right and walk past the kitchen island to the sink.
Pick up the potato on the covered portion of the sink, beside the pump bottle.
Turn around and walk to the refrigerator behind you.
Place the potato in the freezer, wait a moment for it to chill, then remove the potato from the freezer.
Turn around and walk across the kitchen, then turn left at the stove then go to the garbage can, underneath the window, to your right.
Place the potato in the garbage can under the window.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled potato in the garbage can, under the kitchen window.
